*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
*   Record . . . . . M7106                                             *
*   Description  . . Balance Code                                      *
*   Product  . . . . Relationship Pricing                              *
*   Release  . . . . 5.0                                               *
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
SIZE=(21,67), ORIENT=(02,07)
WINDOW BOX
EASEL ON


                       Balance Code - Help

    Valid balance defined within Relationship Pricing.  Valid
    entries are:

      01    Current balance.
      02    Current customer collected.
      03    Current institution collected.
      04    Low balance.
      05    Average balance.
      06    Average collected balance.
      07    Commitment amount.
      08    Credit limit.
      09-15 Reserved.
      16-20 User-defined.  Interfaces must be modified to input
            user-defined balances.
                                                                _
    F12=Cancel                                            M06051S

EASEL OFF
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
FIELD=PFKEY,    PIC='X(01)', ATTR=(DISPLAY,HIDDEN)
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
